{"word":"G3704 - ὅπως - hópōs - hop'-oce - Because","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">ὅπως</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">hópōs</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">hop'-oce</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Because</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>NA / Not Available</span>"},{"paragraph":"பொருட்டு - எச்சம்"},{"paragraph":"as, in what manner, how"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G3739 - ὅς - hós - hos/3739\">G3739</a> nad <a href=\"#/G4459 - πῶς - pōs - poce/4459\">G4459</a>; <i>what</i> (-ever) <i>how</i>, that is, <i>in</i> the <i>manner that</i> (as adverb or conjugation of coincidence, intentional or actual): - because, how, (so) that, to, when.</span>"},{"paragraph":""}]}